about.summary: Python RXP interface - fast validating XML parser

name: pyrxp
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyRXP" %}
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e3c03b88a396744f5c944cb80e48a7eefb4fc9c8e2265ed09b061efb4a635913
  patches:
    # remove existing egg-info directory from tarball
    - remove-egg-info.patch

build:
  number: 1000
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
     - pyRXPU

about:
  home: http://www.reportlab.com
  dev_url: https://bitbucket.org/rptlab/pyrxp/
  license: ReportLab BSD derived
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE.txt'
  summary: Python RXP interface - fast validating XML parser

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - duncanmmacleod
